Dengar baik-baik. Enforce HTTPS itu fundamental, bukan opsional. Kalau Anda masih menjalankan HTTP plain text di produksi, Anda sudah gagal di dasar keamanan.

Ada dua lapisan untuk ini: **Web Server Level** (Paling Direkomendasikan) dan **Application Level** (Middleware). Jangan malas konfigurasi web server hanya karena ingin coding middleware.

### 1. Best Practice: Web Server Level (Nginx)
Ini paling efisien. Jangan bebani aplikasi Anda untuk redirect yang seharusnya ditangani server.

```nginx
server {
    listen 80;
    server_name example.com www.example.com;

    # Enforce HTTPS immediately
    return 301 https://$host$request_uri;
}

server {
    listen 443 ssl http2;
    server_name example.com www.example.com;

    # SSL Configuration (Gunakan Let's Encrypt/Certbot)
    ssl_certificate /etc/letsencrypt/live/example.com/fullchain.pem;
    ssl_certificate_key /etc/letsencrypt/live/example.com/privkey.pem;

    # Security Headers
    add_header Strict-Transport-Security "max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains" always;

    # ... rest of your config
}
```

### 2. Application Level: Laravel (PHP)
Jika Anda terpaksa melakukannya di level aplikasi (misal: behind load balancer yang kompleks), gunakan Middleware.

**File:** `app/Http/Middleware/ForceHttps.php`

```php
<?php

namespace App\Http\Middleware;

use Closure;
use Illuminate\Http\Request;

class ForceHttps
{
    public function handle(Request $request, Closure $next)
    {
        // Penting: Cek header proxy jika berada di belakang Cloudflare/Load Balancer
        if (!$request->secure() && !$request->headers->get('X-Forwarded-Proto') === 'https') {
            return redirect()->secure($request->getPathInfo());
        }

        $response = $next($request);

        // Enforce HSTS Header
        $response->headers->set(
            'Strict-Transport-Security', 
            'max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains', 
            true
        );

        return $response;
    }
}
```
**Registrasi:** Masukkan ke `$middleware` array di `bootstrap/app.php` (Laravel 11) atau `app/Http/Kernel.php` (Laravel 10 ke bawah) agar berjalan global.

### 3. Application Level: Express.js (Node.js)
Jangan pakai package sembarangan. Buat middleware custom yang ketat.

```javascript
const enforceHttps = (req, res, next) => {
    // Cek jika behind proxy (Heroku, AWS ELB, Cloudflare)
    const proto = req.headers['x-forwarded-proto'];

    if (proto !== 'https' && req.secure !== true) {
        return res.redirect(301, `https://${req.headers.host}${req.url}`);
    }

    // Set HSTS Header
    res.setHeader('Strict-Transport-Security', 'max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains');

    next();
};

// Usage
app.use(enforceHttps);
```

### Critical Security Notes (Wajib Baca)

1.  **HSTS (HTTP Strict Transport Security):** Redirect saja tidak cukup. Anda wajib mengirim header `Strict-Transport-Security`. Ini memerintahkan browser untuk *hanya* mengakses via HTTPS di masa depan, mencegah SSL Stripping attacks.
2.  **Proxy Trust:** Jika aplikasi Anda berada di belakang Cloudflare, AWS ELB, atau Nginx Reverse Proxy, variabel `$_SERVER['HTTPS']` atau `req.secure` sering kali salah deteksi. Anda harus mempercayai header `X-Forwarded-Proto`. Pastikan Anda mengkonfigurasi `trusted_proxies` di framework Anda.
3.  **Infinite Loop:** Salah konfigurasi proxy trust akan menyebabkan redirect loop infinity. Tes dulu di staging environment.
4.  **Sertifikat Valid:** Pastikan SSL/TLS certificate Anda valid dan tidak expired. HTTPS dengan cert expired lebih buruk daripada HTTP biasa karena memberi false sense of security.

Amankan server Anda. Jangan ada kompromi untuk enkripsi transit.
